title: Rating of Recipes Prediction
description: Analyzed the relationship between sugar proportion and recipe ratings using Food.com datasets.

title: Pokemon Classification
description: Used Logistic Regression, Support Vector Machine (SVM), and Residual Network 18 (ResNet18) to classsify if a Pokemon has wings or not given an image.

title: Interest Zoning
description: Developed an app to connect event attendees with similar interests within a 1-mile radius, reducing social anxiety.

title: Electric Vehicle Analysis
description: Utilized statistical testing to identify trends in BEV vs. PHEV across Washington counties with 210,000+ EVs.
